Fitness Edge App allows you check various activities. App has features like step counter to calculate your daily steps. Various health calculators to check your daily needs and also guides to various exercises. Remember to always check with your doctor before exercising and seek professional help to ensure correct form of the exercises. The workout videos from Youtube remain the owner\'s, please support them because they do amazing work making them available. Permissions Required: Internet. Step Counter is not supported on all android phones. Please check your phone specification before use. This application requires the internet in order to play Youtube videos that describe each exercise. (The Youtube application needs to be installed in order to view these videos) This application requires the internet in order to use Crashlytics to collect data when and only when the application crashes. The data collected will help to identify the cause of the crash.
